00:18:59.389 --> 00:19:01.850
Father Bobby
would have made a good hit man.

279
00:19:02.017 --> 00:19:05.437
It's a shame we lost him
to the other side.

280
00:19:07.272 --> 00:19:10.901
<i>We were down 7-6 in the last
inning of a sewer-to-sewer stickball game…</i>

281
00:19:11.068 --> 00:19:13.487
