295
00:19:48.021 --> 00:19:49.523
You can take him, Michael.

296
00:19:49.690 --> 00:19:51.400
Yeah, I told you he wasn't shit, baby!

297
00:19:51.566 --> 00:19:53.777
Hey, swallow your tongue,
