302
00:20:03.328 --> 00:20:06.540
Game over, losers.
Cough up the cash. A buck each.

303
00:20:07.207 --> 00:20:08.625
He's no better than you.

304
00:20:08.792 --> 00:20:09.876
He was today.

305
00:20:10.585 --> 00:20:11.920
You let him be.

306
00:20:12.087 --> 00:20:15.090
