394
00:25:28.611 --> 00:25:30.363
I can't hold it!

395
00:25:42.959 --> 00:25:45.128
Stop! God, no!

396
00:26:07.692 --> 00:26:09.486
Damn!

397
00:26:13.740 --> 00:26:16.034
Sweet Jesus.

398
00:26:16.201 --> 00:26:18.244
What have you boys done?

399
00:26:18.411 --> 00:26:20.789
What in the name of God
have you boys done?

400
00:26:20.955 --> 00:26:23.500
I think we just killed a man.

401
00:26:27.962 --> 00:26:31.591
<i>While James Caldwell was
slowly recovering at Saint Clare's Hospital…</i>

402
00:26:31.758 --> 00:26:33.968
<i>… we were charged
with reckless endangerment…</i>

403
00:26:34.135 --> 00:26:36.346
<i>… and remanded
into our parents' custody.</i>

404
00:26:36.513 --> 00:26:37.680
I'm sorry, Dad.

405
00:26:37.847 --> 00:26:40.058
That ain't gonna do you much good.

406
00:26:40.683 --> 00:26:43.895
Take it easy. This is no time to get crazy.

407
00:26:44.646 --> 00:26:47.398
