414
00:27:30.733 --> 00:27:32.861
You still remember what to do?

415
00:27:33.570 --> 00:27:36.948
Easy on the water, heavy on the wine.

416
00:27:37.115 --> 00:27:39.826
And ring the bells whenever
I see someone start to nod off.

417
00:27:40.618 --> 00:27:43.496
Get ready.
We got five minutes to showtime.

418
00:27:55.800 --> 00:27:57.927
I'm gonna miss this.

419
00:28:00.138 --> 00:28:02.432
I'm gonna miss all of this.

420
00:28:03.600 --> 00:28:08.062
I've been doing all I can,
but so far, every door I touch is locked.

421
00:28:11.691 --> 00:28:13.318
I could run.

422
00:28:14.319 --> 00:28:16.196
We all could run.

423
00:28:18.323 --> 00:28:20.283
