424
00:28:20.742 --> 00:28:22.452
Nobody's gonna come looking.

425
00:28:23.828 --> 00:28:26.122
Nobody's gonna care about us.

426
00:28:27.123 --> 00:28:28.124
About where we go.

427
00:28:33.713 --> 00:28:36.799
You run now, you gonna run till you die.

428
00:28:38.718 --> 00:28:43.181
Hiding's not gonna make it go away.
People aren't gonna forget.

429
00:28:44.557 --> 00:28:46.226
You've gotta face this.

430
00:28:51.981 --> 00:28:54.192
I can't, Father.

431
00:28:55.985 --> 00:28:58.321
