432
00:28:59.781 --> 00:29:02.242
I'm too scared to face it.

433
00:29:03.284 --> 00:29:04.702
I'm scared too.

434
00:29:05.245 --> 00:29:07.580
Nobody's more scared than I am…

435
00:29:08.414 --> 00:29:09.874
