1607
01:56:05.918 --> 01:56:07.920
Sure. Let's narrow the place down, then.

1608
01:56:08.087 --> 01:56:11.549
Did you or Mr. Nokes ever hit
any of the boys under your care…

1609
01:56:11.966 --> 01:56:14.552
