1666
02:00:20.423 --> 02:00:22.508
<i>I like it nice and slow.</i>

1667
02:00:23.384 --> 02:00:25.678
<i>You ain't gonna touch me ever again!</i>

1668
02:00:35.479 --> 02:00:36.689
Yes.

1669
02:00:47.491 --> 02:00:48.909
